   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# what is the time increment? Let's look at the metadata for the time coordinate\n",
    "\n",
    "hycom_data.time\n",
    "\n",
    "# looks like it's in hours and so this is hourly. 133 hours seems like a weird amount of time!"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# what is the lat spacing and domain?\n",
    "\n",
    "hycom_data.lat\n",
    "\n",
    "# looks like it goes from 18.12 N to 31.92 N and the spacing is 0.04 degrees. \n",
    "# 1 degree is about 100 km, so that's 4 km "
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "# what about lon?\n",
    "hycom_data.lon\n",
    "\n",
    "# 98 W to 76.4 W in approximately 0.04 steps again, so 4 km"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
